The '''''Deliverance''''' was a ship in the [[Corellian Resistance/Legends|Corellian Resistance]] and the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] that rendezvoused with the [[Emancipator (CR90 corvette)|''Helot's Shackle'']] in order to take over the [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]].

